description:
This is a 17 minute workout called 'High Energy HIIT Row' from the channel Dani Hansen.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity..
The technique difficulty is Advanced and Intermediate.
The effort required is Extreme and Challenging.

Original workout description: Give it all you've got with Dani through 45-second intervals along the Vltava River in Prague. 

Max rhythm: 34, Format: HIIT...
